==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: (The sounds of) broad swords, and wide axes (as when an army sweeps through in battle).

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà dāo kùo fŭ

===Phrase===
'''[[大刀]][[阔]][[斧]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') To handle something with daring and resolve; to be bold and decisive when handling an issue.

#: ''[[南京]][[市]][[将]]'''大刀阔斧'''[[地]][[对]][[延续]][[几]][[十]][[年]][[的]][[行政]][[审批]][[制度]][[进行]][[全面]][[改革]].''

#: ''[[南京]][[市]][[將]]'''大刀闊斧'''[[地]][[對]][[延續]][[幾]][[十]][[年]][[的]][[行政]][[審批]][[制度]][[進行]][[全面]][[改革]].''

===Alternate forms===
[[大刀]][[闊]][[斧]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

